%% Diagram: OOP-R IPC flow between renderer and Viz process
%% Type: sequenceDiagram
sequenceDiagram
    participant Main as Renderer · main thread
    participant CC as Renderer · cc compositor
    participant Worker as Renderer · raster worker
    participant Viz as Viz · GPU process
    participant GPU as GPU driver

    Main->>CC: commit PaintRecord
    CC->>Worker: schedule tile (priority NOW)
    Worker->>Worker: serialize Skia ops to command buffer
    Worker->>Viz: IPC: raster commands + sync token
    Viz->>Viz: Skia (Ganesh / Graphite) replays
    Viz->>GPU: GL / Vulkan / Metal / D3D12 calls
    GPU-->>Viz: texture written
    Viz-->>Worker: signal sync token release
    Viz->>Viz: register texture under mailbox
    CC->>Viz: build CompositorFrame referencing mailbox
    Viz->>GPU: present frame
